               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Metronidazole topical gel USP, 0.75%, is supplied as the following:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>NDC 42254-069-45:  45 g aluminum tube</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Storage conditions:</content> Store at 20° - 25°C (68° - 77°F) [see USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Call your doctor for medical advice about side effects.  You may report side effects to FDA at 1-800-FDA-1088.</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>04584 Rev. 2 10/08</paragraph>
